# ============================================================
#  LaTeX 编译产物（保留源码和 figures/，排除中间文件）
# ============================================================
thesis/latex/*.aux
thesis/latex/*.log
thesis/latex/*.out
thesis/latex/*.bbl
thesis/latex/*.blg
thesis/latex/*.toc
thesis/latex/*.fls
